      • getAtomicPropositions

        public static java.util.Set<org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.agcl.AtomicProposition> getAtomicPropositions(org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.agcl.PSLExpression expr)
        This method collects the set of all atomic propositions present in a PSL formula.

        It uses the PSLAtomicPropositionsSwitch visitor which returns, for each AtomicProposition node in the AST, a singleton set with the node itself. This method collects all the results and returns the union of those singleton sets.

        Parameters:
        expr - a PSL expression
        Returns:
        the set of atomic propositions of a PSL formula
